        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Fairness for Rural Veterans Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill includes construction or acquisition of a nursing home or domiciliary that is from a state with a significant need for beds and is located at least 100 miles away from the nearest existing state home facility as a priority for Department of Veterans Affairs state home facility grants.</p>]]>
        </text>
